    },

    "final_verdict": "Cassie shows promising innovation in making loan guidance more accessible, earning a composite score of 6.75/10. To succeed, the team should prioritize: 1) Implementing robust security measures and regulatory compliance, 2) Developing a more scalable technical infrastructure, 3) Conducting market validation and user testing, 4) Creating a clear business model. The project has potential but requires significant development to become a viable financial service solution. Recommend focusing on security and compliance before scaling the user-friendly features."
